        "original": "よっしゃ、このまま観客席のみんなもラミィのいいところめっちゃ言ってって！",
        "english": "Alright, everyone in the audience, keep saying lots of nice things about Lamy!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:47.000",
        "end": "00:48.200",
        "original": "うちらも言うよ！",
        "english": "We'll say them too!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:48.200",
        "end": "00:49.000",
        "original": "え？うちらも言うの？",
        "english": "Eh? We will too?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
