        "english": "What's going to happen?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:27.400",
        "end": "03:28.400",
        "original": "え、どういうこと？",
        "english": "Eh, what does it mean?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:28.400",
        "end": "03:30.400",
        "original": "やってくれるんじゃないでしょうか、え？！",
        "english": "Isn't she going to do it for us, eh?!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:32.200",
        "end": "03:33.000",
        "original": "これは？",
        "english": "This is...?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:33.200",
        "end": "03:35.000",
        "original": "あ、でもこれはパワーが溜まったんじゃないか？",
        "english": "Ah, but hasn't the power gathered?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:35.400",
        "end": "03:38.000",
        "original": "よしよしよし、ラミィ、元に戻ってくれ！",
        "english": "Good, good, good! Lamy, come back to normal!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:38.200",
        "end": "03:41.200",
        "original": "行け、ねぽらぼ絆ビーム！",
        "english": "Go! NePoLaBo Bonds Beam!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:48.000",
        "end": "03:52.000",
        "original": "元に、戻れ！",
        "english": "Return to normal!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:52.400",
        "end": "03:54.400",
        "original": "ラミィー！！",
        "english": "Lamy!!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:00.000",
        "end": "04:03.000",
        "original": "ラミィ！ラミィ！",
        "english": "Lamy! Lamy!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:04.200",
        "end": "04:06.600",
        "original": "う、う、ラミィは一体...",
        "english": "U-U-Lamy is...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:06.800",
        "end": "04:08.000",
        "original": "あ、元に戻った！",
        "english": "Ah, she's back to normal!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:08.200",
        "end": "04:09.200",
        "original": "よかったー。",
        "english": "Thank goodness.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:09.200",
        "end": "04:11.200",
        "original": "だいふくの力で闇落ちしてたんだよ。",
        "english": "You were corrupted by the power of the Daifuku.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:11.200",
        "end": "04:14.000",
        "original": "いやでも、正直普段のラミィと全然変わんなかったから。",
        "english": "But honestly, you weren't that different from the usual Lamy.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:14.200",
        "end": "04:15.200",
        "original": "元に戻ってよかった。",
        "english": "I'm glad you're back.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:15.200",
        "end": "04:15.800",
        "original": "うん。",
        "english": "Yeah.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:16.000",
        "end": "04:20.400",
        "original": "あ！え、あれ？おお、だいふく！おお。",
        "english": "Oh! Eh? Oh? Whoa, Daifuku! Oh.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:21.400",
        "end": "04:25.800",
        "original": "だいふく、ごめんなさい、ちゃんと見てあげられなくて。",
        "english": "Daifuku... I'm sorry. I didn't take proper care of you.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:26.400",
        "end": "04:28.400",
        "original": "あら、ラミィ...",
        "english": "Oh, Lamy...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:29.000",
        "end": "04:32.400",
        "original": "他人を思いやる気持ちが大事って教わったばっかりなのに。",
        "english": "I just learned that the feeling of thinking of others is important...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:32.600",
        "end": "04:35.000",
        "original": "うまくできなくて、ごめんね。",
        "english": "...but I couldn't do it well. I'm sorry.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:36.000",
        "end": "04:39.600",
        "original": "やっぱりラミィには、だいふくや雪民さんがいないとダメなの。",
        "english": "After all, I need Daifuku and Yukimin-san to be with me.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:40.000",
        "end": "04:42.400",
        "original": "ラミィちゃーん！",
        "english": "Lamy-chaaan!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:44.200",
        "end": "04:47.600",
        "original": "だいふく、ずっとずっと一緒だよ。",
        "english": "Daifuku, we'll be together forever, okay?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:52.100",
        "end": "04:53.900",
        "original": "ホロレンジャー 生誕3Dヒーローショー",
        "english": "Holorenger Birthday 3D Hero Show",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:54.000",
        "end": "05:00.000",
        "original": "完",
        "english": "The End",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      }
    ],
    "model_name": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
  }
